            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Budget teams wanting writing + optimization under $50/mo.</div>
            <a href="/reviews/scalenut/" class="tool-cta-btn">Read review →</a>
